title: Structure Expansion Add-on
author: CrackedCubes
description:
The Structure Expansion Add-On works in YOUR WORLD, adding 110+ new naturally generated structures seamlessly integrated into the overworld! Explore medieval, fantasy, and modern structures floating in the sky or buried deep underground. 

Features:
- 110+ New naturally generated structures
- Works in existing worlds
- Rare ability-enhancing structures
- Custom loot chests
- Medieval, Fantasy, and Modern themes
